      <title>澳大利亚要求与中国有关联的投资者出售其稀土股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/australia-orders-china-linked-investor-to-sell-rare-earths-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚已要求与中国有关的玉晓基金及其关联公司出售其在稀土矿商北方矿业有限公司 (Northern Minerals Ltd.) 的股份，这是美国盟友为对抗亚洲国家在关键矿产领域的主导地位而采取的举措之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/australia-orders-china-linked-investor-to-sell-rare-earths-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 23:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
