      <title>澳大利亚央行被视为唯一面临加息风险的主要央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/rba-seen-as-the-only-other-major-central-bank-at-risk-of-hiking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[货币市场表示，如果通胀未能放缓，澳大利亚央行今年可能别无选择，只能恢复加息，这将成为已几乎结束的疫情后全球紧缩周期的一个潜在异常现象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/rba-seen-as-the-only-other-major-central-bank-at-risk-of-hiking</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
